8) External links
The Official Site, etc. may include links to external websites. Please note that Kodansha will not be responsible for the handling of your Personal Data in such external websites.
9) Community function
Certain sites and services among the Official Site, etc. provide bulletin boards and comment functions. Please do not post any content related to your personal information or the
              personal information of a third party in any service that can be viewed by other users. If you post contents related to your personal information or the personal information of a third
              party in these services, such personal information may be used or misused in a manner that is unintended by the owner of such personal information. In the foregoing case, Kodansha will
              not be liable in any way, and we ask that you exercise due care in using such bulletin boards and comment functions.
10) Social media link buttons
Certain sites and services among the Official Site, etc. provide social media link buttons. When you browse a site provided with social media link buttons, your access data may be
              automatically sent from the corresponding site to the social media even if you do not press the “Like!” button or “Share” button. Please properly use these sites based on your own
              judgment upon understanding the Terms of Use and the Privacy Policy of the social media that you are using.
11) Google Analytics
We use Google Analytics, a service provided by Google, to collect information about how people use the Websites. Google Analytics stores information about what pages you visit, how long
              you are on the sites, how you got there, and what you click on, etc. This information cannot be used to identify who you are. We receive the analysis results from Google and determine
              how you use the Websites therefrom. Such information is managed by Google in accordance with its privacy policy. Please visit the following Google website to obtain further information
              regarding how Google uses cookies.
HOW GOOGLE USES INFORMATION FROM SITES OR APPS THAT USE OUR SERVICES:
