Kodansha may disclose your personal information to a third party for business or commercial purposes. When we disclose personal information to service providers or contractors for
              business or commercial purposes, Kodansha enters into a contract that states such purposes and requires the service providers and contractors to keep such personal information
              confidential and to not use such personal information for any purpose except performing the contract.
